{"tid":1066657,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【港鐵撞車】中環往金鐘要搭港島線 OL接上司溫提早出門","createTime":"2019-03-18T04:31:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T10:32:32.000Z","uid":20913,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7d2e7018069626d31f76a0db5802882312c922c9","tid":1066657,"uid":20913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:31:51.000Z","msg":"港鐵今日(18日)凌晨進行信號系統測試時，2列列車在荃灣線中環站相撞，導致荃灣線來往金鐘站和中環站的服務要全日暫停。不少市民到達中環站才得悉發生事故，令行程受阻，相當不滿。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，荃灣線往中環站的乘客，可於金鐘站轉乘港島線往中環站；而欲搭乘荃灣線的乘客，亦可於中環站搭乘港島線往金鐘站，之後再轉乘荃灣線。<br />\n<br />\n拖篋乘客楊先生今早打算由中環去九龍再返回內地。他指出門口時無特別留意新聞，本來早了半小時出門口，現在因事故反而還遲了半小時，大感無奈，批評港鐵公告不清晰。被問到列車在測試時相撞會否擔心安全問題，他認為有安全隱憂，並稱如若出事「最多咪唔搭囉」。<br />\n<br />\n另一乘客楊先生亦是到了中環站後才得知事故。他指現時中環站不能直接搭乘荃灣線去荃灣，要先搭港島線去金鐘再轉車，令他大失預算。他又大呻到時去了金鐘站不知要等多久才上到車往荃灣，明言如果不對路會搭的士返工，「200幾蚊好貴囉」。<br />\n<br />\n乘客梁先生表示，今早在樂富站上車時，亦「等咗幾轉車」，懷疑港鐵其他線的班次也略受影響，幸好提早出門，才不致返工遲到，本來港鐵無塞車，時間方面容易預算，豈料今晨卻發生列車相撞事故影響行程。另一乘客岑小姐稱，港鐵指示尚算清晰，行程僅多十多分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n由荃灣往中環上班的乘客江小姐表示，今早收到上司溫馨提示，指港鐵有意外服務受阻，故提早上班，聽到站內有廣播呼籲利用東涌線過海，而平日她都是往荔景站再轉東涌線過海往香港站，所以行程沒有改變，今日所見月台的人流及時間也大致與平日一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kPe1zZnhRxUg9seL6es_3Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ1Ni44NDIxMDUyNjMxNTc5/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/y27G_kgB7IZEeQPWqRfhgg--~B/aD00MzQ7dz02MDg7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/a75c4f4d5ec02e60ad6715920cf4c288\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FkPe1zZnhRxUg9seL6es_3Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ1Ni44NDIxMDUyNjMxNTc5%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fy27G_kgB7IZEeQPWqRfhgg--~B%2FaD00MzQ7dz02MDg7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fa75c4f4d5ec02e60ad6715920cf4c288&h=aabe8f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江小姐收到上司溫馨提示提早出門。（曾志恒攝）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190318/mobile/bkn-20190318082735109-0318_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190318%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190318082735109-0318_00822_001.html&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4MzRqNRg6ChYs1Sy50pDDGUM%3D&h=859c9f32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190318/mobile/bkn-20190318082735109-0318_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9062d4d461eb71ab4bcb57ac49abfb262463e405","tid":1066657,"uid":96406,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:32:06.000Z","msg":"可以。"},{"pid":"4105f64b54e6c959a037c2b3305346b80b3526d6","tid":1066657,"uid":17862,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:33:17.000Z","msg":"忟水"},{"pid":"7dddb11cef3810e32e66d9818ddde207c0ff01f8","tid":1066657,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"遲到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b44319f63695f80902fdb7ba075fc4b8cc52bb9","tid":1066657,"uid":134323,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:41:26.000Z","msg":"溫咩撚提<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不知所謂"},{"pid":"dcf2c801311c37ac76a354cffa343cdc8c668c5a","tid":1066657,"uid":42487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:42:00.000Z","msg":"做咩低抄咁影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c868cf0c0c97cce36b2bc51e687bc37c575e16ec","tid":1066657,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:43:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e985c3518bdc65092113f0205d9ce8c2b9813154","tid":1066657,"uid":55533,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"江小姐個樣似琴晚同老細大戰完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3a979d90c392f79d1296aef7d64b200c73450b","tid":1066657,"uid":16733,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20